================================================================================
NOTICE — Preset Place online components are NOT covered by this MIT license
================================================================================

The MIT license above applies to the open-core source code published in this
repository.

The distributed mod binary (the released .jar) additionally bundles the
"Preset Place" online components — the preset sharing service client, its
authentication flow, and the associated online browsing/upload/profile user
interfaces (the classes under `com.trainsystemutilities.presetplace.*` and the
Preset Place online screens). These components are proprietary and are
provided in obfuscated form only. Their source code is NOT published in this
repository and is NOT licensed under MIT.

You may run these proprietary components unmodified as part of the mod for
personal gameplay. You may NOT redistribute them separately, reverse engineer,
decompile, or create derivative works of them, except to the minimum extent
such activity cannot be prohibited under applicable law.

All local, offline functionality of the mod (railway management, wiring,
electrification, routing, timetables, monitors, wiki, and local preset save /
placement) is part of the MIT-licensed open core.
